            <title>[LU-9518] Register lhsmtool_posix  copy fail if enable nodemap</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9518</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1.environment&lt;br/&gt;
If  &quot;lctl nodemap_activate 0&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
=&amp;gt;register copy tool ok then  lfs hsm_archive testfile ok&lt;br/&gt;
If &quot;lctl nodemap_activate 1&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
=&amp;gt;regsiter copy tool fail&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.execute copytool message&lt;br/&gt;
/usr/sbin/lhsmtool_posix --archive 1 -p /mnt/hsmroot /mnt/client&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1494998186.902688 lhsmtool_posix&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;4082&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: action=0 src=(null) dst=(null) mount_point=/mnt/client&lt;br/&gt;
cannot start copytool on &apos;/mnt/client&apos;: Operation not permitted (1)&lt;br/&gt;
1494998186.906422 lhsmtool_posix&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;4082&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: cannot start copytool interface: Operation not permitted (1)&lt;br/&gt;
